query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(q tq s) */ select count(*)
from tag_question AS tq
inner join question AS q
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.score >= 0 AND q.score <= 5
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('acl',
'android-constraintlayout',
'build-automation',
'caliburn.micro',
'database-schema',
'glassfish-3',
'odoo-9',
'ontouchlistener',
'ravendb',
'remote-debugging',
'scrapy-spider',
'vmware',
'wkwebview');
